title: If It’s An Invasion Of The Earth, Of Course It’ll Be Cats Right? - Novel Updates
author: 猫洞　文月
description:
Beyond the distant Milky Way NEKO Star Warrior Cattol  who took on the mission of invading Earth, will be reincarnated into a certain organism on Earth. It was a kitten that Cattol chose. We must control humankind which dominates the earth, surely accomplishing the Earth invasion. Nya ー!

The story is black with bad end, also without much significance(story-wise). Cat lovers Full throttle! (TL: black and bad end were written in kata)>
